QIAP C interface

Introduction

This is the documentation that describes the Application Programmers Interface (API) for the QIAP C interface. It contains a full description of the QIAP C interface and a description of several QIAP-specific CODA functions.

Modules

Each interface is described as a separate module. A separate section contains its general description together with descriptions for all types, variables, functions, etc. that are part of the interface.

  • QIAP C interface
  • QIAP-specific CODA C interface
